{"tid":542079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基辛格數全球威脅源頭： 朝核及中國極權","createTime":"2018-01-27T06:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T07:55:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9115166c1dd9b60d649dd323e97ec61d862471a1","tid":542079,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180127/20286882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20286882&d=Z4SfTW0YYMIcWAN5R97USh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=dce1ca89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F20286882&h=7cb350aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180127/20286882</a><br />\n<br />\n基辛格數全球威脅源頭：<br />\n朝核及中國極權<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180127/large/chris92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180127%2Flarge%2Fchris92.jpg&h=d7bed664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國前國務卿基辛格（Henry Kissinger，圖）前日到國會作證，指北韓是全球最迫切的安全威脅，強調朝鮮半島無核化必須是美國外交政策的「根本」目標。<br />\n<br />\n已94歲高齡的基辛格，跟另一前國務卿舒爾茨、前副國務卿阿米蒂奇等資深外交政策專家，前日在參議院軍事委員會舉行的全球安全威脅小組會前作證。他們指出全球威脅源頭，包括核擴散、中國極權主義、俄羅斯干預美國選舉、俄入侵東歐國家等。<br />\n<br />\n基辛格表示：「對國際安全最迫切的挑戰是北韓核計劃發展。」他指，在國際社會致力阻止「激進國家」發展核力量下，北韓「史無前例」發展出先進核武能力，一旦未能阻止平壤發展核武的步伐，勢將引致亞洲出現軍事競賽，「須做好核武擴散至其他國家的準備」。<br />\n<br />\n基辛格支持繼續向平壤施壓，但警告不能作出軍事選項。惟國際制裁成效成疑，路透社前日引述西歐情報消息指，聯合國安理會去年8月禁止北韓出口煤炭後，北韓仍至少3次海運煤炭到俄羅斯，然後再轉運至日本、南韓。俄駐北韓大使館否認曾購買北韓煤炭或作為中轉站。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"534107659443809c315d857960fd081c78b55788","tid":542079,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"支那世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"fa991fddaa5e74d2f72707d468a2266ebcfe5ac9","tid":542079,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b90c5ac0d248faef9a01d2522a31b743b5e5f1ed","tid":542079,"uid":54095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"世界級外交大師 九十幾歲講野都仲咁清醒"},{"pid":"0e8b6b2f84f1c7e6f9968df0924aca3c4e08d41a","tid":542079,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾 基辛格 講一套做一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01d62777ca38f471db035148acd424494ff35e3","tid":542079,"uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"中國極權咪你呢位美國國師催化出黎囉呀基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a6c519515418ad839ce22f324534ab4f0af5d7","tid":542079,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa991fddaa5e74d2f72707d468a2266ebcfe5ac9","tid":542079,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"連登都好多人想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fd6fca9fdf3d7a4efeccda4429ec32787ca940","tid":542079,"uid":56802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"唔係當年你搞中美建交養隻老虎出嚟就唔會搞到今時今日咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390512d3c52ba3e95ff13691ffbc3a903fc0ad0b","tid":542079,"uid":146340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"明明基辛格放中國出來先"},{"pid":"fba71b34c7df00409f9d59d9207e16b36a2d5564","tid":542079,"uid":48735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif